headline: Allergan Aesthetics Continues Its Mission of Empowering Women Through the Faces of Natrelle® Testimonial Program
summary: Allergan Aesthetics, an AbbVie company (NYSE: ABBV), announced the launch of the Faces of Natrelle® Testimonial Program, a nationwide initiative inviting women to share their real stories and experiences with Natrelle® breast implants to help educate, empower, and support others considering breast surgery.

headline: AbbVie Targets Post Humira Growth With Cell Therapy And RINVOQ Expansion
summary: AbbVie (NYSE:ABBV) has agreed to acquire Capstan Therapeutics to expand its work in in vivo CAR-T cell therapy. The company has also submitted upadacitinib (RINVOQ) for FDA and EMA review as a potential treatment for vitiligo. For you as an investor, these updates relate to AbbVie’s strategy after Humira's patent expiry to position itself as a broad-based biopharma company with exposure to complex immunology and oncology treatments.
